📁 project/
├── main.py               # Python backend with Flask
├── u_p.csv               # Encrypted credentials storage
├── templates/
│   ├── index.html        # Home page
│   ├── save.html         # Save page
│   ├── search.html       # Search + update/delete/copy
│   └── about.html        # About page
├── static/
│   ├── css/
│   │   └── style.css     # Your dark vibrant theme CSS
│   └── js/
│       └── script.js     # Optional client-side JS


🔗 How the frontend connects:
Your HTML pages (save.html, search.html, etc.) live in /templates/

CSS & JS go in /static/

Forms will POST to Flask routes (/save, /search) and Flask will handle all encryption/storage logic